    • Enemy

      public Enemy​(city.cs.engine.World world, java.lang.String type, float walkDistance, org.jbox2d.common.Vec2 startPosition)
      Creates enemy places them in the world with attributes given by the parameters and adds a step listener FlipCharacter to this enemy
      Parameters:
      world - world the enemy is being placed in
      type - the type of enemy that is need for the level, determines its behaviour such as movement and attacks
      walkDistance - distance the enemy is able to move from its start position
      startPosition - start p[osition of the enemy being placed in the world
